description:
Do more in your calendar with one tap. Tempo finds what you need and saves you time and hassles. 

Accolades from TechCrunch, Entrepreneur, Wired, The Guardian, Scobleizer, and more.

•  Full-featured calendar with 5 views, customized alerts, time zone support, search and more. Calendar views are optimized for iPad and iPhone.

•  Easily add events in your own words with natural language input and even with voice like Siri

•  Join conference calls without dialing passcodes.

•  Send “running late” texts or emails to attendees.

•  Create and complete iOS Reminders.

•  Quickly reach people with up-to-date contact details from Google Contacts, Microsoft Outlook Contacts, and iPhone Contacts.

•  Review insights about people before you meet – photos, mutual contacts, Facebook & Google+ posts, LinkedIn details, Tweets, news, Crunchbase, AngelList and more.

•  Find and order Uber rides to your next meeting, intelligently autofilling destinations based on data from your calendars


And more:
•  Get maps, directions and estimated drive time.
•  Review related emails and documents, including Word, Excel, PowerPoint, PDFs and images.
•  Check your flight status, terminal, and gate information.
•  Post birthday greetings on your friends’ Facebook walls.
•  Discover the weather forecast based on your location.
• View company backgrounders including your network there and the latest news.
•  Use smart one-tap alerts to perform actions directly from the lock-screen.
•  Connect multiple email accounts including Exchange, Gmail, iCloud, Hotmail, Outlook, Yahoo, and IMAP.

releaseNotes:
